How do we handle data type SERIAL ?

data type bytea output/input format. Check which we can support (hex/escape).
Hex was introduced in version 9.0. Now hex is default.
http://www.postgresql.org/docs/9.1/static/datatype-binary.html
We might need to do some processing in php depending on how the pg-pdo driver handles binary strings.


