ALTER TABLE ADD COLUMN does not support FIRST/AFTER options

ALTER TABLE ALTER COLUMN will not work as expected.

SELECT column_name, data_type, udt_name, numeric_precision, is_nullable, column_default FROM information_schema.columns WHERE table_name LIKE 'te%' ORDER BY ordinal_position;